1ayp C 83 D 83

A redox-regulated disulphide may form between two units of Phospholipase A2, membrane associated at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

1ayp C 83 D 59

A redox-regulated disulphide may form between two units of Phospholipase A2, membrane associated at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

1ayp A 59 F 59

A redox-regulated disulphide may form between two units of Phospholipase A2, membrane associated at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

1j1a A 59 A 90

Phospholipase A2, membrane associated

1pod A 44 A 97

Phospholipase A2, membrane associated

5g3n A 49 A 90

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Phospholipase A2, membrane associated at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

Phospholipase A2, membrane associated

1kvo F 88 F 90

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Phospholipase A2, membrane associated at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

Phospholipase A2, membrane associated

1pod A 26 A 44

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Phospholipase A2, membrane associated at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.
